title: Pathologic Classic HD-GOG
description:
Pathologic Classic HD (c) Gambitious Digital Entertainment

Release Date : 10/2015
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Genre : Action
Languages : EN/PL/RU
Audio: EN

The original Indie Cult Classic returns fully restored, and more
evocative than ever. Pathologic Classic HD is the Definitive
Edition of the original Cult Classic Psychological First-Person
Survival game. The game represents a unique and unforgettable
experience as it transports players in a weird town which crouches,
ominous, in the far reaches of an ancient steppe.

For more info go to : http://www.gog.com/game/pathologic_classic_hd
